The paper discusses the use of blockchain to improve the security and decentralization of network backbone components such as PKI, BGP, and DNS. This topic falls under the categories of computer security (cs.CR), computer networks (cs.NI), distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC), software engineering (cs.SE), and digital libraries (cs.DL).
